title: The.Return.Of.Bruno.Bruce.Willis.Mockumentary.Blues.HBO.1987.com
description:
This is \"THE RETURN OF BRUNO\".  I also have a basically lossless copy of the CD of anyone is interested. It\&#039;s over 400 MB at over 1400kb/s. Pretty f-ing bitchin!

It is a relatively HQ VHSrip I made a couple days ago.

It is personally one of the funniest things I\&#039;ve seen. I would call it hellaciously hilarious.

The return of Bruno is a Mockumentary about a guy named Bruno Radolini who is a famous Blues singer/harmonica player....

It has all kinds of stuff from American Bandstand performances, to woodstock, to A homemade psychedelic era video, and a live concert from the 80s...

It has cameos by Paul Stanley of KISS, Jon Bon jovi, Sir REginald Dwight (elton john), the Bee Gees, ringo Star, Michael J. Fox, etc.


Bruce willis Is actually a very talented harmonica player, which is awesome. 

He also has a Prince Valiant haircut at some point in the DVD.

Thanx for watching this and please seed...
